[THWACKS]

00:05:51.900 --> 00:05:54.567
[GRUNTS]

00:05:54.567 --> 00:05:57.267
[COUGHING]

00:05:57.267 --> 00:05:59.267
- [GRUNTING]
- [BLOWS LAND]

00:05:59.267 --> 00:06:00.333
